des:
In this number guessing game, you will meet a spinosaurus named Stella that has lots of dinosaur friends. Stella will ask you to guess how many dinosaurs showed up when she invited them over to your house. You can guess between 0 and 30. You will continue to guess higher or lower until you get it correct! How fast can you guess it?

During the game you will hear dinosaur sounds and be rewarded when you guess it correctly. The game is fun for all ages.
